  "datePublished": "2026-03-06",
  "description": "An ***introduction*** is the opening section of an essay that orients the reader to the subject, states or implies the [thesis](../../../terms/thesis.md), and creates a reason to keep reading. It is the counterpart of the [conclusion](./conclusion.md): the introduction sets up the essay's question; the conclusion shows what the essay has found.",
